(26985, 'Silvigo 50mg 5 f.c. tabs.', 'سيلفيجو 50مجم 5 اقراص', '', '24', 'Sildenafil', 'Memphis', 'Tab', 'أقراص', '', 'Tonic for men', '50mg', 'Sildenafil is a phosphodiesterase-5 (PDE5) inhibitor that is predominantly employed for two primary indications:
